'''Spych Boat''' is a music visualizer world that attempts to recreate the intense visuals of music festivals such as DEFQON.1.

It is a very popular world to bring new VRChat players to, as its intense musically synched visuals are a great showcase of the unique experiences available in VR.

The first half of the experience is started via a button at the back of the boat. 
Once the song finishes, the boat lands on an island. At the back of the island, there is a large button on the beach that starts the second half of the experience.

The songs featured are "Getsix - Sky Fracture (VIP)" and "Frequencerz - Victory Forever"